Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 突然叫你们出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻的父亲居然反对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才选这个时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁伯父不在 对伯母发起攻势
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯母的话一定会站在我们这边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 日记也借给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是为了面麻的话 一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 又瞒着她去她家 被发现的话肯定会生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天集君和知利子也来了 我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打...打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是好兆头么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火箭烟花？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从孩子他爸那里听到的时候吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不是很好么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家亲密得聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊 小时候和面麻一起做呢 烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 芽衣子她...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个... 如果烟花能升空的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻... 我想芽衣子她也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么伯父他...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的是亲密无间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 没有啦... 说不上是亲密无间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子会很羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被同伴抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说芽衣子她会高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还不是排除芽衣子 你们自己沉溺其中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯...伯母？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子已经...不在世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们却完全没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天你们也和芽衣子一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了那孩子的日记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间...停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那孩子 还是和以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:04:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么你们却像这样长大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有芽衣子她...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子 芽衣子她一人...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们差不多该告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见 手不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有些可怕啊 面麻她妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 或许一直在憎恨着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是出生以来第一次呢 被别人这么憎恨着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的父母心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻的愿望这种傻事适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 这样的话面麻她...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该注意到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是在配合着你 配合着可悲的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也做过模仿的事情 没有资格说你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我不会做像你这种将自己的伤痛强加于他人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样吗 你被过去所束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害面麻的父母 还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...一定是在说自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的人 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一直相信的 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信着面麻的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我一个人来实现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是大家一起的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为大家都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是实际沟通后觉得并没有什么改变 吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 无论怎么没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有[大家]这种集体观念了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很久之前就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为缺少了面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是[大家]不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来实现也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会和之前一样继续下去的 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险的啊 还在脱鞋子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只有我一人也要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只有我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 又找份打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 体力活薪水比较高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气色不是很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 因为没有睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都过着吃了睡的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡眠储存还很充分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么变得这么拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么对面麻...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁...仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你 水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个 营养剂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平静多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧 这事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳也受了许多伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事还是停手吧 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在工作中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候也是 不希望你走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我要说有损形象的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候我松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳说不喜欢面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这样我很差劲 但却有点窃喜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却那样跑开了 不就是说最喜欢面麻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起一直很心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅那一瞬间的窃喜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害了面麻 造成了那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于仁碳... 无法原谅对于喜欢仁碳的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是...还是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是要走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好奇怪啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的面麻出现在仁碳身边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望实现的话面麻不就会消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明喜欢面麻 她消失也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:10:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指甲好黑 我去拿牙签
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 愿望实现后 面麻会...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 对不起 对不起 马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是面麻的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 有这么痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs24}注释：卡通「佛兰德斯的狗」改编自国际知名作品 Ouida "A Dog of Flanders"  温馨感人 知性感性并重 藉由少年龙龙的心路历程 见证生命的酸甜苦辣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想起了佛兰德斯的狗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs24}注释：Patrasche：「佛兰德斯的狗」故事里狗的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Patrasche的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Patrasche？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛兰德斯 以前...重播的片子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么 这谎话也太扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 我想Patrasche一定很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs24}注释：Nello：「佛兰德斯的狗」故事里主人公的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它被Nello疼爱着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被当做是朋友不是吗 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为失去了面麻 面麻的母亲才所以一直怀恨着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸣一直在责备自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子一定也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连波波也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在罪恶感中得不到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看得到面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯独我被面麻拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么的不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 已经到这个时间了 今天打工 啊不 学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是塔子的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我去 等我下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先去下面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若只有我能看到面麻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就有必须去完成面麻愿望的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生锈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我不去学校 老爸也从不说我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为是已经对我死心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是 所谓的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个... 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要是关于打工的事情 你不用在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 是想说去本间家的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你到底想说哪一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我根本不知道仁碳到底想道歉什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 把香拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究敌不过父母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳大清早晨什么都没说就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？是波波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算面麻的父母是那种表态 总不能让仁碳一个人做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为超和平克星会和以前那样进行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}喂 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}你们吵架了吗？到底怎么啦 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}总之 面麻的事我是相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是只有仁碳一个人能看到她 就算别人都不相信 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？无声电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那个 宿海君正在打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号码显示的是宿海家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海打来的无言电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但听到一些沙沙的沙暴一样的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能你会认为我很傻 但会不会不是宿海打来的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城同学 不请假就不来上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没从安城同学说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天明明跟拳击俱乐部的同僚举行肌肉聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后应该怎样面对小鸣好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有 该道歉的是冒昧打扰的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大妈基本不出门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像不想见到其他人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我知道那是失去姐姐后非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 却感觉很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的人竟是我的母亲 感觉很难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 父母究竟都在想些什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉着最痛苦的是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的父母 呃 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我没权去说别人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还剩一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我当时很小 几乎没有对姐姐的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:18:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是有些事 是记得的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪君不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你姐姐我啊 是超和平克星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去保护大家的和平哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以聪君要保护好咱家 明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她让我保护家...虽这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那毫无生气的家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 仁碳也来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天都干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么...打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没打电话吗 打到我们那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五点左右有无声电话打到我家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无声？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是什么？又要把面麻搬出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个时间我和我老爸都不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能真是面麻...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么跟什么呀你 老是面麻面麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也让我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻不是在吗 所以也让我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.30,0:19:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷静点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 又！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你别这样了好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太差劲了 宿海 都这时候了 你还在装幽灵玩？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为何要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在那吗？仁碳 面麻在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快别玩了 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 请稍等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 求你了 请快停止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经对面麻所做过的事情 永远不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻道歉什么的 绝对是骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻是绝对不会原谅我们曾经所做过的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日记
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为 为什么 明明没有风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 这到底是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 波波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和已经长大的大家在秘密基地里玩耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吵架哦 超和平克星要一直相亲相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 给我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是面麻的字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 回答正确
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是面麻么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:51.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}何ページも費やして　つづられた僕らの気分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:58.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうしてか一行の　空白を埋められない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:07.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}押花のしおり挟んで　君と転がす 使い捨ての自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:14.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}忘れかけのレンガを　積み上げた場所に行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.46,0:01:19.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}海を見渡す坂を駆け上って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:24.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}こわいくらいに青い空と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.42,0:01:32.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}右手にサイダー　左手はずっと君を探している
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:39.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}そうやって今は僕の方へ　問いつめることもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:46.80,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}まだ二人はすぐそこにいるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:54.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうかまたあえますようになんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:02:03.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}どうかしてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:51.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}填寫了好幾頁 我們那連綿的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:58.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2\be1}卻為何填補不了那空白的一行
